node.title: Body found off Coromandel's Whangapoua, believed to be missing fisherman
node.description: Search and rescue teams began looking for the missing man on Friday.
node.content: ["A body has been found in the search for a fisherman missing off Whangapoua in Coromandel.\n", "Search and rescue teams began looking for the missing man on Friday afternoon after he failed to return to the Whangapoua boat ramp.", "A boat was located on Saturday but the man remained missing.\u00a0", "Now, police say a body has been found.", "\"The body was located yesterday evening at around 5:40pm by a Coastguard fixed-wing plane, south of Kennedy Bay,\" a police spokesperson said on Sunday, adding it's believed the man is the missing fisherman.", "\"Next of kin are being notified and police's thoughts are with his family.\"", "Police thanked everyone involved in the search."]
